","display_username":"Eugene Kozlov","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"Core developer","title_is_group":false,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":484,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false},{"id":21229,"name":"Taymindis Woon","username":"Taymindis","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/taymindis/{size}/941_2.png","created_at":"2017-10-13T12:46:36.970Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eHi Eugene,\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAttached Screen Shot For References\u003cimg src=\"//cdck-file-uploads-global.s3.dualstack.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/1X/46dea60ff30e7e12c1c487b509e391145926ef87.png\" alt=\"29 PM\" width=\"607\" height=\"500\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI couldn’t find out E_SCROLLBARCHANGED event, is this define at other header file? The purpose I want to make it scrollbar move physically.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eShould I use ListView instead of scrollbar view?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e","post_number":3,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-10-13T12:46:36.970Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":2,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":37,"readers_count":36,"score":22.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":3653,"topic_slug":"difficulty-to-handling-scrollview","display_username":"Taymindis Woon","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"username":"Eugene","name":"Eugene Kozlov","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/eugene/{size}/902_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":848,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false},{"id":21230,"name":"Eugene Kozlov","username":"Eugene","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/eugene/{size}/902_2.png","created_at":"2017-10-13T13:21:59.371Z","cooked":"\u003caside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"3653\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"title\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"quote-controls\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cimg alt width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://sjc6.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/taymindis/40/941_1.png\" class=\"avatar\"\u003e Taymindis:\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ehelloText-\u0026gt;SetPosition\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWell, start with removing this line. You shouldn’t set position and size of your elements manually if you use automatic layout (vertical or horizontal).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003caside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"3653\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"title\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"quote-controls\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cimg alt width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://sjc6.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/taymindis/40/941_1.png\" class=\"avatar\"\u003e Taymindis:\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003echatContentElement-\u0026gt;SetSize(_scrollV-\u0026gt;GetSize());\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHere is the same. You literally forced your content to have the same size as your window. If you use ScrollView, you probably want the content to be \u003cem\u003ebigger\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003caside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"3653\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"title\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"quote-controls\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cimg alt width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://sjc6.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/taymindis/40/941_1.png\" class=\"avatar\"\u003e Taymindis:\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI couldn’t find out E_SCROLLBARCHANGED event, is this define at other header file?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n\u003caside class=\"onebox githubblob\"\u003e\n  \u003cheader class=\"source\"\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/blob/ee054a1507cb3518c57d4ebc43cfd6dc93de9a27/Source/Urho3D/UI/UIEvents.h#L213\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003egithub.com\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003c/header\u003e\n  \u003carticle class=\"onebox-body\"\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/urho3d/Urho3D/blob/ee054a1507cb3518c57d4ebc43cfd6dc93de9a27/Source/Urho3D/UI/UIEvents.h#L213\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eurho3d/Urho3D/blob/ee054a1507cb3518c57d4ebc43cfd6dc93de9a27/Source/Urho3D/UI/UIEvents.h#L213\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cpre class=\"onebox\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"lang-h\"\u003e\u003col class=\"start lines\" start=\"203\" style=\"counter-reset: li-counter 202 ;\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e}\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e/// UI progressbar value changed\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eURHO3D_EVENT(E_PROGRESSBARCHANGED, ProgressBarChanged)\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e{\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eURHO3D_PARAM(P_ELEMENT, Element);              // UIElement pointer\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eURHO3D_PARAM(P_VALUE, Value);                  // float\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e}\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e/// UI scrollbar value changed.\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c